      "title": "About \u2014 Full PBR",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# BrainDead \u2014 Image \u2192 Full PBR\n\nTurn any character/image into game-ready **PBR maps** (albedo, normal, roughness, metallic, AO + packed ORM/ARM).\n\n**Flow:** Load Image \u2192 BD Remove Background (silhouette) ; full image \u2192 Lotus-2 **Depth** + **Normal** (masked, neutral bg) ; BD SAM3 Multi-Prompt finds **metal** zones \u2192 BD Derive PBR Maps \u2192 albedo / normal / roughness / metallic / AO / packed ORM+ARM.\n\nNotes: feed the FULL image to Lotus-2 (best detail, no halo) \u2014 the subject mask cleans the bg AFTER. AO is derived from depth; metallic = low-sat/high-lum INSIDE the SAM3 metal zone. Lotus-2 + SAM3 auto-download on first run.\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** \u2014 created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) \u00b7 [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) \u00b7 [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) \u00b7 [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)"
      ]
    }
